list.name: Changes
list.comment: ### REFACTORING ### 1. Change names of classes, variables and databases ("match" -> "game", etc.). 2. Move text constants to common class. 3. Fix bug related to calculation of timeLefts at the end of the game. 4. Improve boardState to simplifiedBoardStateString conversion. 5. Add draw check in case of insufficient material. 6. Minor changes.

task.summary: ### Basic game-master service implementation (with SSE) ### 1. Partially implement chess game logic with subscription on chess moved based on Server Sent Events (not the best option). 2. Move to using username as id for User class (instead of long id). 3. Replace PostgreSQL by MongoDB in game-master service.
